					<description><![CDATA[Copy Trading is a game-changer in the trading world, allowing less experienced individuals, or “followers” to automatically copy the trades of successful professionals, making financial markets more accessible. Professional traders, or &#8220;providers,&#8221; can share strategies and earn additional income. This system connects providers with followers, eliminating the need for complex strategies or constant market monitoring, [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.atfx.com.bz/en/analysis/trading-strategies/copy-trading">Copy Trading</a> is a game-changer in the trading world, allowing less experienced individuals, or “followers” to automatically copy the trades of successful professionals, making financial markets more accessible. Professional traders, or &#8220;providers,&#8221; can share strategies and earn additional income. This system connects providers with followers, eliminating the need for complex strategies or constant market monitoring, while enabling followers to trade with confidence and ease.</p>
<h2>How CopyTrade Works?</h2>
<h3>Step-by-Step Process for Followers:</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Step 1</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Selecting a Provider</strong></p>
<p>Followers choose a provider whose strategies match their goals and risk tolerance. <a href="https://www.atfx.com.bz/en/trading-platforms/atfx-copytrade" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ATFX CopyTrade</a> platforms offer performance statistics, including trading history, success rate, and market focus, to help followers make informed decisions.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Step 2</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Allocating Funds</strong></p>
<p>Once a provider is selected, followers allocate funds to copy the provider’s trades. The amount invested can vary depending on the follower’s budget and desired exposure to the provider&#8217;s strategies.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Step 3</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Trade Replication in Real-Time</strong></p>
<p>After funds are allocated, trades made by the provider are automatically copied in real time. This allows the follower to mirror the provider’s trades, from entry to exit, proportionally based on the funds allocated.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Step 4 </strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Flexibility in Settings</strong></p>
<p>Followers can adjust certain settings, such as the percentage of their portfolio to copy, stop-loss limits, or even choose to stop copying a provider at any time. This flexibility ensures followers can manage risk according to their preferences.</p>
<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-large wp-image-46240 aligncenter" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/How-CopyTrade-Works-For-Followers-and-Providers-1024x526.webp" alt="How CopyTrade Works For Followers and Providers" width="800" height="411" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/How-CopyTrade-Works-For-Followers-and-Providers-1024x526.webp 1024w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/How-CopyTrade-Works-For-Followers-and-Providers-300x154.webp 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/How-CopyTrade-Works-For-Followers-and-Providers-768x395.webp 768w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/How-CopyTrade-Works-For-Followers-and-Providers.webp 1344w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<h3>Step-by-Step Process for Providers:</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Step 1 </strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Setting Up an Account</strong></p>
<p>To become a provider, traders must set up an account with a platform that supports CopyTrade. This typically involves providing a track record of successful trades and demonstrating experience and reliability.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Step 2 </strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Requirements for Providers</strong></p>
<p>Providers often need to meet specific criteria, such as a minimum trading history and performance benchmarks, to ensure they are qualified to offer their strategies to followers.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Step 3 </strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Trade Replication for Followers</strong></p>
<p>Once set up, a provider’s trades are automatically replicated by followers who have chosen to copy them. Providers’ earnings will depend on the success of their trades and the number of followers who choose to copy them.</p>
<div class="article-banner article-banner__dark" style="display: flex; background-color: #103d91; border-radius: 20px; color: #fff; padding: 20px; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin: 20px 0; flex-wrap: wrap;">
<div class="article-banner-content" style="flex: 1; margin-right: 20px; min-width: 250px;">
<p><span style="font-size: 30px; color: #fff; font-weight: bold;">Follow. Copy. Profit. It&#8217;s That Simple!</span></p>
