										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.atfx.com.bz/en/trading-platforms/atfx-copytrade">ATFX CopyTrade</a> is an automated service that is designed to allow traders to invest passively in the forex and Second Contract market by copying other successful professional traders on the ATFX copy trading leaderboard. This service aims to shorten the learning curve for newbie traders by providing them with an opportunity to mirror the trades of other traders that are already achieving success in the forex/Second Contract market.</p>
