<p dir="ltr">There are three parties to the copy trading service: the Provider, the copy trade broker (ATFX) and the Follower (a passive investor who copies the trades). Anyone can be a Signal Provider, provided you can demonstrate that you have a long history of profitable trading and solid risk management.</p>
